entry.title: WindowsAzure.Storage
entry.summary: This package contains a class library with the Windows Azure Storage Proxy Cloud Services, and a WebActivator enabled class with the default configuration.

m:properties.d:Description: This package contains a class library with the Windows Azure Storage Proxy Cloud Services, and a WebActivator enabled class with the default configuration.
m:properties.d:Tags: Storage WindowsAzure DPE
m:properties.d:Title: Windows Azure Storage Proxy Cloud Services

entry.title: WindowsAzure.Storage
entry.summary: A client library for working with Windows Azure storage services including blobs, tables, and queues.

m:properties.d:Description: This client library enables working with the Windows Azure storage services which include the blob service for storing binary and text data, the table service for storing structured non-relational data, and the queue service for storing messages that may be accessed by a client.
m:properties.d:Tags: Microsoft Azure Storage Table Blob Queue Scalable windowsazureofficial
m:properties.d:Title: Windows Azure Storage

m:properties.d:Description: This client library enables working with the Microsoft Azure storage services which include the blob and file service for storing binary and text data, the table service for storing structured non-relational data, and the queue service for storing messages that may be accessed by a client. For this release see notes - https://github.com/Azure/azure-storage-net/blob/master/README.md and https://github.com/Azure/azure-storage-net/blob/master/changelog.txt Microsoft Azure Storage team's blog - http://blogs.msdn.com/b/windowsazurestorage/
m:properties.d:Tags: Microsoft Azure Storage Table Blob File Queue Scalable windowsazureofficial
m:properties.d:Title: Windows Azure Storage
